{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2014}} {{Use Irish English|date=April 2014}} {{Refimprove|date=June 2009}} {{Infobox Radio Station | name = Clare FM |image=CLare FM logo.png | airdate = 10 September 1989 | frequency = 95.2 [[megahertz|MHz]] - 96.6 [[MHz]], [[DAB in Ireland|DAB]] | slogan = ''Sounds like you'' | area = [[County Clare]], [[Republic of Ireland|Ireland]] | format = [[Adult Oriented Pop Music]] with local [[news]], [[sports]] and specialist programmes | owner = Clare Community Radio Holdings Ltd. | website = http://www.clare.fm/ }} '''Clare FM''' is an [[Republic of Ireland|Irish]] [[radio station]] which broadcasts to [[County Clare]] and the surrounding areas.
