'''Fabula''' is a literary award in [[Slovenia]] awarded each year for the best collection of short prose in [[Slovene language|Slovene]] published in the previous two years. It has been bestowed since 2006 by the national newspaper house [[Dnevnik (Slovenia)|Dnevnik]] at the Fabula World Literatures festival that takes place every spring in [[Ljubljana]]. The winner also receives a financial award.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.drustvo-dsp.si/si/drustvo_slovenskih_pisateljev/prireditve_nagrade/648/detail.html |title=Slovene Writers' Association site |language=Slovenian |work=Slovene writers' portal |publisher=DSP Slovene Writers' Association |accessdate=25 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111115103229/http://www.drustvo-dsp.si/si/drustvo_slovenskih_pisateljev/prireditve_nagrade/648/detail.html |archivedate=15 November 2011 |df= }}</ref>
