'''Leƒëan''' or '''Legen''' was an ancient, often described as magical, [[city]] from the [[Croats|Croatian]] [[mythology]] and [[folklore]].<ref>{{cite book |title=Na≈°a narodna epika |authorlink=Tomislav Maretiƒá |last=Maretiƒá |first=Tomislav |author2=Vladan Nediƒá  |pages=39‚Äì40 |year=1966 |origyear=1909 |publisher=Nolit |oclc=1368666 }}</ref> It features in [[Ivana Brliƒá-Ma≈æuraniƒá]]'s ''[[Croatian Tales of Long Ago]]'', a collection of Croatian [[fairy tales]] dramatised into short stories.

