====Order: [[Carnivora]] (carnivorans)==== ---- [[Image:Hydrurga leptonyx edit1.jpg|thumb|[[Leopard seal]]]] There are over 260 species of carnivorans, the majority of which feed primarily on meat. They have a characteristic skull shape and dentition.
