'''''Special Assignment''''' is an investigative current affairs programme on [[SABC]]. Since August 1998<ref>[[#dupreez2003|Du Preez 2003]]: 254</ref> the programme has covered news events in South Africa and beyond, often disclosing criminal activities and atrocities unknown to the public. Ashraf Garda is the shows current host.<ref>SABC2012.http://www.sabc.co.za/wps/portal/SABC/SABCARTICLE?id=3188a40046565324bb10ffa11538544e&page_from=PRESS.</ref> The Show is screened weekly on SABC3 at 21:30 GMT.<ref>SABC3 official page 2012-02-27.http://www.sabc3.co.za/show/special-assignment/.</ref>
